<style>
  .gal-intro { text-align: center; max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem var(--gutter) 2rem; }
  .gal-intro h1 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); color: var(--color-dark); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .gal-intro p { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-style: italic; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 2; color: var(--color-mid-dark); }
  .gal-slide { position: relative; min-height: 65vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-size: cover; background-position: center; overflow: hidden; }
  .gal-slide-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(20,18,25,0.45) 0%, rgba(20,18,25,0.65) 100%); }
  .gal-slide-text { position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center; color: rgba(255,250,245,0.95); max-width: 550px; padding: 2.5rem 3rem; background: rgba(20,18,25,0.3); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px); border-radius: 16px; }
  .gal-slide-text h2 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.2rem); margin-bottom: 1rem; text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); }
  .gal-slide-text p { font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.6vw, 1.08rem); line-height: 2; text-shadow: 0 1px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
  .gal-slide-whisper { font-style: italic; opacity: 0.7; font-size: 0.9rem !important; letter-spacing: 0.15em; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
  .gal-slide-accent { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-style: italic; font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem) !important; margin-top: 1.2rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .gal-ornament { text-align: center; color: var(--color-warm); opacity: 0.4; letter-spacing: 0.5em; padding: 2rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .lightbox { display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 9999; background: rgba(20,18,22,0.92); backdrop-filter: blur(6px); align-items: center; justify-content: center; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; }
  .lightbox.active { display: flex; opacity: 1; }
  .lightbox-img { max-width: 92vw; max-height: 88vh; object-fit: contain; border-radius: 6px; box-shadow: 0 12px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.25s ease; }
  .lightbox-img.switching { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.96); }
  .lightbox-close { position: absolute; top: 1rem; right: 1.2rem; background: none; border: none; color: rgba(255,250,245,0.7); font-size: 2rem; cursor: pointer; width: 48px; height: 48px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: color 0.2s; z-index: 2; }
  .lightbox-close:hover { color: rgba(255,250,245,1); }
  .lightbox-nav { position: absolute; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); background: none; border: none; color: rgba(255,250,245,0.6); font-size: 2.5rem; cursor: pointer; padding: 1rem; transition: color 0.2s; z-index: 2; }
  .lightbox-nav:hover { color: rgba(255,250,245,1); }
  .lightbox-nav--prev { left: 0.5rem; }
  .lightbox-nav--next { right: 0.5rem; }
  .lightbox-counter { position: absolute; bottom: 1rem; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); color: rgba(255,250,245,0.5); font-size: 0.85rem; font-family: var(--font-body); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .gal-slide { min-height: 50vh; } }
</style>

<div class="gal-intro">
  <h1>Galerie</h1>
  <p>Erinnere Dich,<br>
  Du bist mehr, als Du denkst.<br>
  In dir lebt die Erde,<br>
  in dir ruht der Himmel.<br>
  Zwischen Herz und Atem<br>
  zeigt sich das Ganze.<br>
  Werde still ...<br>
  und erinnere dich.</p>
</div>

<div class="gal-slide" style="background-image: url('/images/wasser.jpg');">
  <div class="gal-slide-overlay"></div>
  <div class="gal-slide-text">
    <p class="gal-slide-whisper">spüre und fühle</p>
    <h2>Du bist Wasser</h2>
    <p>... trinke ... fliesse ... sprudle ...<br>
    ... hüpfe über Steine ...<br>
    ... tauche auf und ab ...<br>
    ... reinige … weine …<br>
    ... las gehen, was gehen will ...<br>
    ... erfrische dich… ... ströme …</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="gal-slide" style="background-image: url('/images/feuer.jpg');">
  <div class="gal-slide-overlay"></div>
  <div class="gal-slide-text">
    <p class="gal-slide-whisper">spüre und fühle</p>
    <h2>Du bist Feuer</h2>
    <p>... brenne ... lodere ... sprühe ...<br>
    ... reinige ... entfalte ... verändere ...<br>
    ... dehne dich aus ... verwandle ...<br>
    ... knistere ... inspiriere ...<br>
    ... leuchte ... wärme … ... tanze …</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="gal-slide" style="background-image: url('/images/luft.jpg');">
  <div class="gal-slide-overlay"></div>
  <div class="gal-slide-text">
    <p class="gal-slide-whisper">spüre und fühle</p>
    <h2>Du bist Luft</h2>
    <p>... atme ruhig ... fliege leicht ... steige auf …<br>
    ... flüstere … … lass dich tragen ...<br>
    ... fantasiere ... beobachte ...<br>
    ... fokussiere ... ... kläre ... ... entscheide ...</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="gal-slide" style="background-image: url('/images/erde.jpg');">
  <div class="gal-slide-overlay"></div>
  <div class="gal-slide-text">
    <p class="gal-slide-whisper">spüre und fühle</p>
    <h2>Du bist Erde</h2>
    <p>... sei geerdet … vertraue … empfange ...<br>
    … danke … ... schenke ... behüte ...<br>
    ... pflege ... wachse ... ernte ...<br>
    ... achte die Fülle ...<br>
    ... heile ... beschütze … nähre dich ...</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="gal-slide" style="background-image: url('/images/bewusstsein.jpg');">
  <div class="gal-slide-overlay"></div>
  <div class="gal-slide-text">
    <h2>Sei eins mit Deinem Bewusstsein</h2>
    <p>... verbinde Dich mit Dir ... zentriere Dich ... im Herzen ...<br>
    ... schau nach Innen ... lausche nach Aussen ... atme ruhig ...<br>
    … geniesse das Sein … lass Dich inspirieren ...<br>
    ... sei achtsam im Hier und Jetzt ...</p>
    <p class="gal-slide-accent">ICH BIN HIER JETZT</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="gal-slide" style="background-image: url('/images/closing.jpg');">
  <div class="gal-slide-overlay"></div>
  <div class="gal-slide-text">
    <h2>Freue Dich,<br>sei lebendig und glücklich,<br>liebe</h2>
    <p class="gal-slide-accent">Es ist Dein Geburtsrecht.</p>
  </div>
</div>

